<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ration Distribution</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .output {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Ration Distribution</h1>
        <p>If the fingerprint machine doesn't work, use the following authentication number:</p>
        <div id="output" class="output">
            Fingerprint is not taken. Use this random number for authentication: {{ randomNumber }}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
